e:[["$","title","0",{"children":"How to Improve OHSMS following ISO 45001 Clause 10"}],["$","meta","1",{"name":"description","content":"How to Improve OHSMS following ISO 45001 Clause 10\n\t\t\t\tWhen reviewing the requirements of ISO 45001 certification in Dubai, UAE to create your"}],["$","meta","2",{"name":"keywords","content":"How to Improve OHSMS following ISO 45001 Clause 10"}],["$","meta","3",{"property":"og:title","content":"How to Improve OHSMS following ISO 45001 Clause 10"}],["$","meta","4",{"property":"og:description","content":"How to Improve OHSMS following ISO 45001 Clause 10\n\t\t\t\tWhen reviewing the requirements of ISO 45001 certification in Dubai, UAE to create your"}],["$","meta","5",{"property":"og:url","content":"https://wizms.net/how-to-improve-ohsms-following-iso-45001-clause-10"}],["$","meta","6",{"property":"og:type","content":"article"}],["$","meta","7",{"property":"article:published_time","content":"2026-01-02T06:30:56+00:00"}],["$","meta","8",{"name":"twitter:card","content":"summary"}],["$","meta","9",{"name":"twitter:title","content":"How to Improve OHSMS following ISO 45001 Clause 10"}],["$","meta","10",{"name":"twitter:description","content":"How to Improve OHSMS following ISO 45001 Clause 10\n\t\t\t\tWhen reviewing the requirements of ISO 45001 certification in Dubai, UAE to create your"}],["$","link","11",{"rel":"icon","href":"/favicon.ico"}],["$","$L18","12",{}]]
10:["$","p","7",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"It is crucial to note that this clause is the same in all ISO management system standards. So, if you have an integrated management system that meets the standards of ISO 9001:2015 certification, Quality Management System, or ISO 14001:2015 certification in Dubai, UAE, Environmental Management System, you may utilize a single corrective action procedure for process nonconformities."}]
11:["$","p","8",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Clause 10.3 - Ongoing development"}]
12:["$","p","9",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"The final sub clause addresses how to continually enhance the OH&SMS for appropriateness, adequacy, and effectiveness; in other words, how do you make your OH&SMS better? So, whereas clause 10.1 discusses increasing OH&S performance, clause 10.3 discusses enhancing OH&S procedure. How do you enhance your procedures so that they operate better inside your OHSMS and, as a result, make your workplace's OH&S culture more effective? How can you improve the OH&S management process?"}]
13:["$","p","10",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"For example, you might select a less dangerous substance to replace one that you now use. This might come in the form of a proposal from your supplier regarding a cleaning solution they have created that is less dangerous to personnel than the one you are presently using. Appendix A.10.3 provides examples of continuous improvement concerns that might be incorporated in an OH&SMS for additional information. To know the importance of ISO Certification, checkout the article."}]
14:["$","p","11",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"One of the guiding ideas underlying ISO standards is an improvement."}]
15:["$","p","12",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"One of the main ideas underlying below the ISO Certification in UAE for management system standards is an improvement, and identifying methods to improve the system is entrenched in many of the activities. This is why, following paragraph 9, performance review, we are monitoring, measuring, analyzing, and evaluating data — so that we can make data-driven decisions to improve the system. Companies that wish to adopt an OH&SMS do so to enhance their organization's OH&S performance, and the standards of clause 10 offer a strong foundational framework to make this happen."}]
16:["$","p","13",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Checkout the article to know about the ISO 45001:2015 Mandatory List"}]
17:["$","footer",null,{"className":"mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"flex flex-wrap gap-2","children":[["$","span","0",{"className":"text-xs font-semibold text-gray-600 bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded","children":"How to Improve OHSMS following ISO 45001 Clause 10"}]]}]}]
